# =============================================================================
# HSB task-management-agents — operator environment
# =============================================================================
# Variables consumed via the `hsb.settings.*` modules. The new settings surface
# is the canonical reader; some legacy code paths still read the old vars
# directly via os.environ until those sites migrate.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Runtime authentication (RuntimeSettings, CodexSettings)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Required: Claude OAuth token from `claude setup-token`. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is
# refused at startup (G1 — see hsb.settings.runtime.assert_oauth2_only).
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=your_anthropic_oauth_token_here

# Optional: Codex authentication directory. Defaults to /root/.codex for the
# project's Docker container (root user). Host developers running locally
# override to e.g. $HOME/.codex.
# CODEX_HOME=/root/.codex

# Optional: explicit path to the `codex` binary. When unset, PATH lookup is
# used. Override only if Codex lives outside PATH.
# CODEX_PATH_OVERRIDE=/usr/local/bin/codex

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Linear / GitHub authentication (LinearSettings, GitHubSettings)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Optional: Linear API key — fallback for headless/CI when OAuth via
# mcp-remote (D-01) is not available.
# LINEAR_API_KEY=your_linear_api_key_here

# Optional: GitHub PAT for non-interactive `gh auth login --with-token`. When
# set, `make auth-github` uses the token instead of the device flow. Scope:
# `repo`. Persisted to the hsb-gh-auth named volume.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_personal_access_token_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Per-agent runtime selection (RuntimeSettings)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# One env var per known agent. Value: "claude" (default) or "codex".
# Field names are full-word slugs to keep env vars self-explanatory.
#
# The Work Item Orchestrator is hard-blocked from "codex" because the
# stateful ClaudeSDKClient session has no Codex equivalent yet —
# HSB_RUNTIME_WORK_ITEM_ORCHESTRATOR=codex raises at construction with a
# project-specific explanation.
#
# Legacy `HSB_RUNTIME_WIO`, `HSB_RUNTIME_QA`, `HSB_RUNTIME_UAT` are still read
# by `hsb.agents._sdk_options.resolve_runtime()` until those callsites
# migrate to RuntimeSettings.

# HSB_RUNTIME_BACKLOG=claude                  # backlog agent
# HSB_RUNTIME_WORK_ITEM_ORCHESTRATOR=claude   # hard-blocked from "codex"
# HSB_RUNTIME_QUALITY_ASSURANCE=claude        # QA review agent
# HSB_RUNTIME_USER_ACCEPTANCE_TESTING=claude  # UAT agent
# HSB_RUNTIME_RISK=claude
# HSB_RUNTIME_GIT=claude
# HSB_RUNTIME_BUILDER=claude
# HSB_RUNTIME_INTELLIGENCE=claude
# HSB_RUNTIME_LINEAR=claude

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Operational tuning (OrchestratorSettings)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Main Orchestrator claim-debounce in milliseconds. Default 200.
# HSB_CLAIM_DELAY_MS=200

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Test fixtures (TestFixtureSettings) — opt-in, skipped when unset
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# hsb-test-fixture GitHub repo URL — Builder + Git agent integration tests.
# Operator must own the repo (gh CLI authenticated with `repo` scope).
# See .planning/phases/02-core-execution-agents/02-FIXTURE-REPO.md
# HSB_TEST_FIXTURE_URL=https://github.com/<YOUR_GITHUB_USER>/hsb-test-fixture

# Local filesystem path to the cloned hsb-test-fixture repo. Used by
# integration tests that need a real working tree.
# HSB_TEST_FIXTURE_PATH=/path/to/hsb-test-fixture

# Opt in to the live Codex integration test
# (tests/integration/test_backlog_codex_live.py). Without this set, the test
# is skipped. Requires CODEX_HOME and HSB_RUNTIME_BACKLOG=codex to also be set.
# HSB_LIVE_CODEX=1

# Linear test work-item / issue IDs for end-to-end integration tests.
# TEST_WORK_ITEM_ID=LIN-123
# LINEAR_TEST_ISSUE_ID=LIN-456

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Host-only — do NOT put in this file (it is loaded into the container)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# HSB_PROJECT scopes Docker Compose volumes/containers per org for multi-org
# isolation. It must be exported in your shell BEFORE invoking `make`, e.g.:
#   export HSB_PROJECT=org-acme
#   make auth-linear && make up
# Default: "task-management-agents". See scripts/_lib.sh.
